{"data": [{"id": "4743229", "title": "Gold And Silver Take Off On Surprise Rally", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/514059136/image_514059136.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Precious metals\" data-id=\"514059136\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5184px\" height=\"3456px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/514059136/image_514059136.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/514059136/image_514059136.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/514059136/image_514059136.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/514059136/image_514059136.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/514059136/image_514059136.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/514059136/image_514059136.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/514059136/image_514059136.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/514059136/image_514059136.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">claffra</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>Originally published on December 9, 2024</em></p> <p><em>\u201cDon\u2019t look a gift horse in the mouth.\u201d</em></p> <p>That was my first thought on seeing gold up about $45 and silver jumping 4% this morning while other markets weren\u2019t confirming the moves.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/514059136/image_514